  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个短链接服务的完整交互流程。核心有三个环节：用户注册、创建短链、以及最后的跳转重定向。参与方包括浏览器端、Drogon API Pod，还有PostgreSQL数据库。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User Browser",
        "Drogon API Pod",
        "PostgreSQL",
        "Registration",
        "Create Short Link",
        "Redirect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。注册流程里，浏览器发POST请求到/register之后，API层需要做密码哈希再落库对吧？然后返回201和token。创建短链的时候需要带上Bearer token做鉴权吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "POST /register",
        "Hash password",
        "INSERT INTO users",
        "201 Created",
        "token",
        "POST /shorten",
        "Auth: Bearer token"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，注册环节返回token，创建短链时必须校验这个Bearer token。API验证通过后会生成短码，写入links表，然后返回201带上code和short_url。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bearer token",
        "Validate & Generate Code",
        "INSERT INTO links",
        "code",
        "short_url"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我把注册和创建短链的前两个Note标注画好了。现在处理第三个环节——跳转重定向。用户访问短码链接时，API去数据库查原始URL，然后返回302？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Note over User, API",
        "GET /{code}",
        "SELECT url FROM links",
        "302 Found"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，302的Location头里放destination URL。这里注意数据库返回的是原始长链接，API再组装成302响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Location: destination",
        "Return Destination URL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我检查了一下，刚才写的时候把第三个Note的位置标错了，标到了API和DB之间。应该覆盖User和API这两个参与者才对，我修正一下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Note over User, API"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有个小细节，所有数据库返回的消息用虚线箭头，表示异步响应。另外三个Note分别标注阶段编号：1. Registration、2. Create Short Link、3. Redirect，方便阅读。",
      "elements_involved": [
